# =============================================================================
# Sparkle Cookie — CODE-ONLY repository
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# This repo intentionally tracks ONLY our custom code, data, and documentation.
# It does NOT track the licensed third-party asset packs (PuzzleMatchKit,
# GuiPackAnimalWorld) or any binary art/audio. A fresh clone will NOT build
# until those packs are re-imported locally — see docs/SETUP.md. This is by
# design, to avoid redistributing licensed assets.
# =============================================================================

